snippet.title: Friday Reads, a mini haul and the Lambda Literary Prize
snippet.description:
Books Mentioned
Era of Ignition by Amber Tamblyn
Hollywood's Eve by Lili Anolik
Crystals by Katie-Jane Wright
How to Write an Autobiographical Novel by Alexander Chee
Freshwater by Akwaeke Emezi
Amateur by Thomas Page McBee
The Unpunished Vice by Edmund White
Leah on the Offbeat by Becky Albertalli
The Inexplicable Logic of my Life by Benjamin Alire Saenz
Muse of Nightmares by Laini Taylor
Aerie by Maria Dhavana Headley

Lambda Literary Prize
https://www.lambdaliterary.org
